242
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:34,120
Un voyage d'affaires d'une semaine au minimum.

243
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:35,440
Xinhai ?

244
00:11:36,519 --> 00:11:38,039
Un ensemble de tours d'ordinateurs là-bas,

245
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,600
